Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「莫笑浪有意…」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.45,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,かけじやそでの…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,序盘的时候 印象还比较清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算牌面朝下了 多少还能拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在互送牌逐渐变多的后半…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底注意力能有多集中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「…多情徒恨痴」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:56.81,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…の　ぬれもこそすれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:06.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「草庐东南望 离尘宇治山」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:06.40,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}わがいほは　みやこのたつみ　しかぞすむ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明记住了那张的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…没有以往的那种敏捷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有了自信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为她一直都只靠模糊的记忆…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.09,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢千早!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿是「欲寻」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.81,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,658)}はるす
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「飞练」…「名盛」…「大江」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.39,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,658)}たき
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.39,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,658)}これ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.39,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,658)}おおえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「春情」…「谁为」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.31,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,658)}こひ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.31,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,658)}たれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要移动一下牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.91,writings2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(427,611)\frz351.854}等会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「人皆谓避世 我自沉幽禅」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:05.50,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,よをうぢやまと　ひとはいふなり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「岁晚山愈寒…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.55,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やまざとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「激流戏浅水…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.22,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,せをはやみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是往常陪我练习时的那个太一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「川尚同归处 人定复举杯」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:50.17,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,われてもすゑに　あはむとぞおもふ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「芙蓉帐犹暖…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.01,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ながからむ　こころ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「惠露霑艾草 然诺…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:58.47,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}ちぎりおきし　させもがつゆを…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围手…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了后半还能记住牌的正确位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:08.69,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「苇生难波滩 节短聚益稀」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:08.69,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なにはがた　みじかきあしの　ふしのまも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿…拿对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:13.66,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「怨君心何忍 残生…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:13.66,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}あはでこのよを　すぐしてよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想过成为名人 所以输了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「输了也没关系」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.80,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「朝寒初霜降 淡染秋庭…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:29.80,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}こころあてに　をらばやをらむ　はつし…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能没关系!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你面前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不甘心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我们来了这么一场比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后自己就一言不发地走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有那种人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么好的朋友 又有能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的啊? 书桌小子的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是超完美的嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦 书桌小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次考试也要拿第一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拿第一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我拿了第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也进不了那个圈子里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有了一丁点兴趣的话 要不要加入歌留多部?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多这东西…我怎么可能玩得来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没那种天赋!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只会学习…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有书桌这一片天地啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还是去跟别人比你能赢的东西吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我…就算赌上全部青春」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「也不可能变得比新更强」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩歌留多的天赋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使很吃力 我也还是在玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使会输 我也还是在玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…获胜的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是何等的开心啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要选同伴的话 比起歌留多的天才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更愿意选在榻榻米上 不断努力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么榻榻米 什么歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「即使很吃力 我也还是在玩!」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「即使会输 我也还是在玩!」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
